text: Yalli hebeltô baxa isi nafsih mahaysitinnaay, kaadu kalah qibaadá cakkisita Yalli kaâ luk mayan, aka Yalli kaâ luk suginnay, toysa kulli Yalli isi ginó haysitak yeneeh, gari-garu keenik korisak yeneeh, aamuk yenen addunyah amoytiitih innah, Yalli koros kaa edde weelossu haytaamak saytunnooweh
